summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 5, 6, 7 and west 10 feet of Lot 4, Block 1, Cloverdale Addition, and the north one-half of Lot 2, Block 3, Ashford's Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-211 and 17-157, respectively.
